text:
1. Prepare equipment
2. Approach the diving board
3. Stand at the edge of the diving board
4. Take a deep breath
5. Bend the knees
6. Push off the diving board
7. Extend the arms forward
8. Tuck the body into a pike position (optional)
9. Enter the water headfirst
10. Straighten the body
11. Extend the arms to the sides
12. Kick the legs to maintain momentum
13. Surface from the water
